1871#         Raises:
1872#             FileNotFoundError: If no log files can be found in the log directory.
1873#         """

1876#         # Filter files to include only log files (adjust the extension accordingly)
1877#         log_files = [f for f in files if f.endswith(".log")]
1878#         # Check if there are any log files
